title: Tyra Banks Interview and More

description:
Today on the show we had living legend Tyra Banks stop by where she spoke about her new project Model Land, her experience modeling, juggling being a mother and a entrepreneur and more. Also Charlamagne gave another Floridian Donkey of the Day and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
